Node List Door History file:

  1.00 10th June 1993

Finished version 1.00                   

  1.01 11th June 1993

Only a day after the 1st release and here comes the second!
+ Now puts 'Mail Only' instead of tel. no. for MO flag BBS.
+ Also "Node Down" and "Node on hold" reported as well.
+ Config enhanced for Nodelist Path.
+ Screen made a little more attractive!
+ ~100% faster as it is now compiled.

  1.02 15th June 1993

+ Case insensitive searching
+ More? Prompts
+ CTRL D to abort search
: Bug fixes (Node down problem)

  1.02b 18th June 1993

+ EOF character used rather than [1a]
+ Basic version for RISC OS 2 users

  1.03 26th June 1993

: Bug fixes (Didn't realise that Region and Zone entries were
             host numbers as well, whoops!)
: Changed abort to CTRL-C as ARCbbs style

Richard...